 |:;;;;;;::;::::::::|||||||||      /
 |.##||||.|,,,,,,,,,........|  &lt;--/
 |.##||||&#039; &#039;&#039;&#039;&#039;&#039;&#039;&#039;&#039;&#039;|||||||||
 |--------------------------|
 |!!!!!!!!!!^^||^^!!!!!!!!!!|  &lt;------- Metallic Distribution Shelf (MDS)
 |!!!!!!!!!!^^||^^!!!!!!!!!!|
