 |!!!!!!!!!!^^||^^!!!!!!!!!!|
 |--------------------------|
 |!!!!!!!!!!^^||^^!!!!!!!!!!|  &lt;------- Metallic Distribution Shelf (MDS)
 |!!!!!!!!!!^^||^^!!!!!!!!!!|
 |--------------------------|
 |!!!!!!!!!!^^||^^!!!!!!!!!!|  &lt;------- Metallic Distribution Shelf (MDS)
 |!!!!!!!!!!^^||^^!!!!!!!!!!|
 +--------------------------+


